==Box office==
''The Shaukeens'' collected {{INRConvert|32.36|c}} from the domestic box office and was declared "Average".<ref name="BH The Shaukeens">{{cite web|url=http://www.koimoi.com/box-office/the-shaukeens-2nd-week-box-office-collections/|title=The Shaukeens: 2nd Week Box Office Collections|accessdate=20 November 2014|website=Koimoi.com}}</ref><ref name="Koimoi">{{cite web|url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/moviemicro/boxoffice/id/596434|title=The Shaukeens|accessdate=20 November 2014}}</ref>

